109// Checks if object meets the condition
110// Can have CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_NONE && !mReferenceId if called from a special event (ie: SmartAI)
111bool Condition::Meets(ConditionSourceInfo& sourceInfo) const
112{
113 ASSERT(ConditionTarget < MAX_CONDITION_TARGETS);
114 WorldObject* object = sourceInfo.mConditionTargets[ConditionTarget];
115 // object not present, return false
116 if (!object)
117 {
118 TC_LOG_DEBUG("condition", "Condition object not found for %s", ToString().c_str());
119 return false;
120 }
121 bool condMeets = false;
122 switch (ConditionType)
123 {
124 case CONDITION_NONE:
125 condMeets = true; // empty condition, always met
126 break;
127 case CONDITION_AURA:
128 {
129 if (Unit* unit = object->ToUnit())
130 condMeets = unit->HasAuraEffect(ConditionValue1, ConditionValue2);
131 break;
132 }
133 case CONDITION_ITEM:
134 {
135 if (Player* player = object->ToPlayer())
136 {
137 // don't allow 0 items (it's checked during table load)
138 ASSERT(ConditionValue2);
139 bool checkBank = ConditionValue3 ? true : false;
140 condMeets = player->HasItemCount(ConditionValue1, ConditionValue2, checkBank);
141 }
142 break;
143 }
144 case CONDITION_ITEM_EQUIPPED:
145 {
146 if (Player* player = object->ToPlayer())
147 condMeets = player->HasItemOrGemWithIdEquipped(ConditionValue1, 1);
148 break;
149 }
150 case CONDITION_ZONEID:
151 condMeets = object->GetZoneId() == ConditionValue1;
152 break;
153 case CONDITION_REPUTATION_RANK:
154 {
155 if (Player* player = object->ToPlayer())
156 {
157 if (FactionEntry const* faction = sFactionStore.LookupEntry(ConditionValue1))
158 condMeets = (ConditionValue2 & (1 << player->GetReputationMgr().GetRank(faction))) != 0;
159 }
160 break;
161 }
162 case CONDITION_ACHIEVEMENT:
163 {
164 if (Player* player = object->ToPlayer())
165 condMeets = player->HasAchieved(ConditionValue1);
166 break;
167 }
168 case CONDITION_TEAM:
169 {
170 if (Player* player = object->ToPlayer())
171 condMeets = player->GetTeam() == ConditionValue1;
172 break;
173 }
174 case CONDITION_CLASS:
175 {
176 if (Unit* unit = object->ToUnit())
177 condMeets = (unit->getClassMask() & ConditionValue1) != 0;
178 break;
179 }
180 case CONDITION_RACE:
181 {
182 if (Unit* unit = object->ToUnit())
183 condMeets = (unit->getRaceMask() & ConditionValue1) != 0;
184 break;
185 }
186 case CONDITION_GENDER:
187 {
188 if (Player* player = object->ToPlayer())
189 condMeets = player->getGender() == ConditionValue1;
190 break;
191 }
192 case CONDITION_SKILL:
193 {
194 if (Player* player = object->ToPlayer())
195 condMeets = player->HasSkill(ConditionValue1) && player->GetBaseSkillValue(ConditionValue1) >= ConditionValue2;
196 break;
197 }
198 case CONDITION_QUESTREWARDED:
199 {
200 if (Player* player = object->ToPlayer())
201 condMeets = player->GetQuestRewardStatus(ConditionValue1);
202 break;
203 }
204 case CONDITION_QUESTTAKEN:
205 {
206 if (Player* player = object->ToPlayer())
207 {
208 QuestStatus status = player->GetQuestStatus(ConditionValue1);
209 condMeets = (status == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE);
210 }
211 break;
212 }
213 case CONDITION_QUEST_COMPLETE:
214 {
215 if (Player* player = object->ToPlayer())
216 {
217 QuestStatus status = player->GetQuestStatus(ConditionValue1);
218 condMeets = (status == QUEST_STATUS_COMPLETE && !player->GetQuestRewardStatus(ConditionValue1));
219 }
220 break;
221 }
222 case CONDITION_QUEST_NONE:
223 {
224 if (Player* player = object->ToPlayer())
225 {
226 QuestStatus status = player->GetQuestStatus(ConditionValue1);
227 condMeets = (status == QUEST_STATUS_NONE);
228 }
229 break;
230 }
231 case CONDITION_ACTIVE_EVENT:
232 condMeets = sGameEventMgr->IsActiveEvent(ConditionValue1);
233 break;
234 case CONDITION_INSTANCE_INFO:
235 {
236 Map* map = object->GetMap();
237 if (map->IsDungeon())
238 {
239 if (InstanceScript const* instance = ((InstanceMap*)map)->GetInstanceScript())
240 {
241 switch (ConditionValue3)
242 {
243 case INSTANCE_INFO_DATA:
244 condMeets = instance->GetData(ConditionValue1) == ConditionValue2;
245 break;
246 //case INSTANCE_INFO_GUID_DATA:
247 // condMeets = instance->GetGuidData(ConditionValue1) == ObjectGuid(uint64(ConditionValue2));
248 // break;
249 case INSTANCE_INFO_BOSS_STATE:
250 condMeets = instance->GetBossState(ConditionValue1) == EncounterState(ConditionValue2);
251 break;
252 case INSTANCE_INFO_DATA64:
253 condMeets = instance->GetData64(ConditionValue1) == ConditionValue2;
254 break;
255 }
256 }
257 }
258 break;
259 }
260 case CONDITION_MAPID:
261 condMeets = object->GetMapId() == ConditionValue1;
262 break;
263 case CONDITION_AREAID:
264 condMeets = object->GetAreaId() == ConditionValue1;
265 break;
266 case CONDITION_SPELL:
267 {
268 if (Player* player = object->ToPlayer())
269 condMeets = player->HasSpell(ConditionValue1);
270 break;
271 }
272 case CONDITION_LEVEL:
273 {
274 if (Unit* unit = object->ToUnit())
275 condMeets = CompareValues(static_cast<ComparisionType>(ConditionValue2), static_cast<uint32>(unit->getLevel()), ConditionValue1);
276 break;
277 }
278 case CONDITION_DRUNKENSTATE:
279 {
280 if (Player* player = object->ToPlayer())
281 condMeets = (uint32)Player::GetDrunkenstateByValue(player->GetDrunkValue()) >= ConditionValue1;
282 break;
283 }
284 case CONDITION_NEAR_CREATURE:
285 {
286 condMeets = GetClosestCreatureWithEntry(object, ConditionValue1, (float)ConditionValue2, bool(!ConditionValue3)) ? true : false;
287 break;
288 }
289 case CONDITION_NEAR_GAMEOBJECT:
290 {
291 condMeets = GetClosestGameObjectWithEntry(object, ConditionValue1, (float)ConditionValue2) ? true : false;
292 break;
293 }
294 case CONDITION_OBJECT_ENTRY_GUID:
295 {
296 if (uint32(object->GetTypeId()) == ConditionValue1)
297 {
298 condMeets = !ConditionValue2 || (object->GetEntry() == ConditionValue2);
299
300 if (ConditionValue3)
301 {
302 switch (object->GetTypeId())
303 {
304 case TYPEID_UNIT:
305 condMeets &= object->ToCreature()->GetSpawnId() == ConditionValue3;
306 break;
307 case TYPEID_GAMEOBJECT:
308 condMeets &= object->ToGameObject()->GetSpawnId() == ConditionValue3;
309 break;
310 default:
311 break;
312 }
313 }
314 }
315 break;
316 }
317 case CONDITION_TYPE_MASK:
318 {
319 condMeets = object->isType(ConditionValue1);
320 break;
321 }
322 case CONDITION_RELATION_TO:
323 {
324 if (WorldObject* toObject = sourceInfo.mConditionTargets[ConditionValue1])
325 {
326 Unit* toUnit = toObject->ToUnit();
327 Unit* unit = object->ToUnit();
328 if (toUnit && unit)
329 {
330 switch (static_cast<RelationType>(ConditionValue2))
331 {
332 case RELATION_SELF:
333 condMeets = unit == toUnit;
334 break;
335 case RELATION_IN_PARTY:
336 condMeets = unit->IsInPartyWith(toUnit);
337 break;
338 case RELATION_IN_RAID_OR_PARTY:
339 condMeets = unit->IsInRaidWith(toUnit);
340 break;
341 case RELATION_OWNED_BY:
342 condMeets = unit->GetOwnerGUID() == toUnit->GetGUID();
343 break;
344 case RELATION_PASSENGER_OF:
345 condMeets = unit->IsOnVehicle(toUnit);
346 break;
347 case RELATION_CREATED_BY:
348 condMeets = unit->GetCreatorGUID() == toUnit->GetGUID();
349 break;
350 default:
351 break;
352 }
353 }
354 }
355 break;
356 }
357 case CONDITION_REACTION_TO:
358 {
359 if (WorldObject* toObject = sourceInfo.mConditionTargets[ConditionValue1])
360 {
361 Unit* toUnit = toObject->ToUnit();
362 Unit* unit = object->ToUnit();
363 if (toUnit && unit)
364 condMeets = ((1 << unit->GetReactionTo(toUnit)) & ConditionValue2) != 0;
365 }
366 break;
367 }
368 case CONDITION_DISTANCE_TO:
369 {
370 if (WorldObject* toObject = sourceInfo.mConditionTargets[ConditionValue1])
371 condMeets = CompareValues(static_cast<ComparisionType>(ConditionValue3), object->GetDistance(toObject), static_cast<float>(ConditionValue2));
372 break;
373 }
374 case CONDITION_ALIVE:
375 {
376 if (Unit* unit = object->ToUnit())
377 condMeets = unit->IsAlive();
378 break;
379 }
380 case CONDITION_HP_VAL:
381 {
382 if (Unit* unit = object->ToUnit())
383 condMeets = CompareValues(static_cast<ComparisionType>(ConditionValue2), unit->GetHealth(), static_cast<uint32>(ConditionValue1));
384 break;
385 }
386 case CONDITION_HP_PCT:
387 {
388 if (Unit* unit = object->ToUnit())
389 condMeets = CompareValues(static_cast<ComparisionType>(ConditionValue2), unit->GetHealthPct(), static_cast<float>(ConditionValue1));
390 break;
391 }
392 case CONDITION_WORLD_STATE:
393 {
394 condMeets = ConditionValue2 == sWorld->getWorldState(ConditionValue1);
395 break;
396 }
397 case CONDITION_PHASEID:
398 {
399 condMeets = object->IsInPhase(ConditionValue1);
400 break;
401 }
402 case CONDITION_TITLE:
403 {
404 if (Player* player = object->ToPlayer())
405 condMeets = player->HasTitle(ConditionValue1);
406 break;
407 }
408 case CONDITION_SPAWNMASK:
409 {
410 condMeets = ((1 << object->GetMap()->GetSpawnMode()) & ConditionValue1) != 0;
411 break;
412 }
413 case CONDITION_UNIT_STATE:
414 {
415 if (Unit* unit = object->ToUnit())
416 condMeets = unit->HasUnitState(ConditionValue1);
417 break;
418 }
419 case CONDITION_CREATURE_TYPE:
420 {
421 if (Creature* creature = object->ToCreature())
422 condMeets = creature->GetCreatureTemplate()->type == ConditionValue1;
423 break;
424 }
425 case CONDITION_REALM_ACHIEVEMENT:
426 {
427 AchievementEntry const* achievement = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievement(ConditionValue1);
428 if (achievement && sAchievementMgr->IsRealmCompleted(achievement, std::numeric_limits<uint32>::max()))
429 condMeets = true;
430 break;
431 }
432 case CONDITION_IN_WATER:
433 {
434 if (Unit* unit = object->ToUnit())
435 condMeets = unit->IsInWater();
436 break;
437 }
438 case CONDITION_TERRAIN_SWAP:
439 {
440 condMeets = object->IsInTerrainSwap(ConditionValue1);
441 break;
442 }
443 default:
444 condMeets = false;
445 break;
446 }
447
448 if (NegativeCondition)
449 condMeets = !condMeets;
450
451 if (!condMeets)
452 sourceInfo.mLastFailedCondition = this;
453
454 bool script = sScriptMgr->OnConditionCheck(this, sourceInfo); // Returns true by default.
455 return condMeets && script;
456}

458uint32 Condition::GetSearcherTypeMaskForCondition() const
459{
460 // build mask of types for which condition can return true
461 // this is used for speeding up gridsearches
462 if (NegativeCondition)
463 return (GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_ALL);
464 uint32 mask = 0;
465 switch (ConditionType)
466 {
467 case CONDITION_NONE:
468 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_ALL;
469 break;
470 case CONDITION_AURA:
471 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_CREATURE | GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
472 break;
473 case CONDITION_ITEM:
474 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
475 break;
476 case CONDITION_ITEM_EQUIPPED:
477 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
478 break;
479 case CONDITION_ZONEID:
480 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_ALL;
481 break;
482 case CONDITION_REPUTATION_RANK:
483 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
484 break;
485 case CONDITION_ACHIEVEMENT:
486 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
487 break;
488 case CONDITION_TEAM:
489 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
490 break;
491 case CONDITION_CLASS:
492 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_CREATURE | GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
493 break;
494 case CONDITION_RACE:
495 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_CREATURE | GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
496 break;
497 case CONDITION_SKILL:
498 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
499 break;
500 case CONDITION_QUESTREWARDED:
501 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
502 break;
503 case CONDITION_QUESTTAKEN:
504 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
505 break;
506 case CONDITION_QUEST_COMPLETE:
507 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
508 break;
509 case CONDITION_QUEST_NONE:
510 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
511 break;
512 case CONDITION_ACTIVE_EVENT:
513 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_ALL;
514 break;
515 case CONDITION_INSTANCE_INFO:
516 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_ALL;
517 break;
518 case CONDITION_MAPID:
519 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_ALL;
520 break;
521 case CONDITION_AREAID:
522 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_ALL;
523 break;
524 case CONDITION_SPELL:
525 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
526 break;
527 case CONDITION_LEVEL:
528 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_CREATURE | GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
529 break;
530 case CONDITION_DRUNKENSTATE:
531 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
532 break;
533 case CONDITION_NEAR_CREATURE:
534 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_ALL;
535 break;
536 case CONDITION_NEAR_GAMEOBJECT:
537 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_ALL;
538 break;
539 case CONDITION_OBJECT_ENTRY_GUID:
540 switch (ConditionValue1)
541 {
542 case TYPEID_UNIT:
543 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_CREATURE;
544 break;
545 case TYPEID_PLAYER:
546 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
547 break;
548 case TYPEID_GAMEOBJECT:
549 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_GAMEOBJECT;
550 break;
551 case TYPEID_CORPSE:
552 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_CORPSE;
553 break;
554 case TYPEID_AREATRIGGER:
555 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_AREATRIGGER;
556 break;
557 default:
558 break;
559 }
560 break;
561 case CONDITION_TYPE_MASK:
562 if (ConditionValue1 & TYPEMASK_UNIT)
563 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_CREATURE | GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
564 if (ConditionValue1 & TYPEMASK_PLAYER)
565 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
566 if (ConditionValue1 & TYPEMASK_GAMEOBJECT)
567 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_GAMEOBJECT;
568 if (ConditionValue1 & TYPEMASK_CORPSE)
569 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_CORPSE;
570 if (ConditionValue1 & TYPEMASK_AREATRIGGER)
571 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_AREATRIGGER;
572 break;
573 case CONDITION_RELATION_TO:
574 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_CREATURE | GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
575 break;
576 case CONDITION_REACTION_TO:
577 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_CREATURE | GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
578 break;
579 case CONDITION_DISTANCE_TO:
580 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_ALL;
581 break;
582 case CONDITION_ALIVE:
583 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_CREATURE | GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
584 break;
585 case CONDITION_HP_VAL:
586 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_CREATURE | GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
587 break;
588 case CONDITION_HP_PCT:
589 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_CREATURE | GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
590 break;
591 case CONDITION_WORLD_STATE:
592 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_ALL;
593 break;
594 case CONDITION_PHASEID:
595 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_ALL;
596 break;
597 case CONDITION_TITLE:
598 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
599 break;
600 case CONDITION_SPAWNMASK:
601 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_ALL;
602 break;
603 case CONDITION_GENDER:
604 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
605 break;
606 case CONDITION_UNIT_STATE:
607 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_CREATURE | GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
608 break;
609 case CONDITION_CREATURE_TYPE:
610 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_CREATURE;
611 break;
612 case CONDITION_REALM_ACHIEVEMENT:
613 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_ALL;
614 break;
615 case CONDITION_IN_WATER:
616 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_CREATURE | GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_PLAYER;
617 break;
618 case CONDITION_TERRAIN_SWAP:
619 mask |= GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_ALL;
620 break;
621 default:
622 ASSERT(false && "Condition::GetSearcherTypeMaskForCondition - missing condition handling!");
623 break;
624 }
625 return mask;
626}

628uint32 Condition::GetMaxAvailableConditionTargets() const
629{
630 // returns number of targets which are available for given source type
631 switch (SourceType)
632 {
633 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_SPELL:
634 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_SPELL_IMPLICIT_TARGET:
635 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_CREATURE_TEMPLATE_VEHICLE:
636 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_VEHICLE_SPELL:
637 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_SPELL_CLICK_EVENT:
638 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_GOSSIP_MENU:
639 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_GOSSIP_MENU_OPTION:
640 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_SMART_EVENT:
641 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_NPC_VENDOR:
642 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_SPELL_PROC:
643 return 2;
644 default:
645 return 1;
646 }
647}

649std::string Condition::ToString(bool ext /*= false*/) const
650{
651 std::ostringstream ss;
652 ss << "[Condition ";
653 ss << "SourceType: " << SourceType;
654 if (SourceType < CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_MAX)
655 ss << " (" << ConditionMgr::StaticSourceTypeData[SourceType] << ")";
656 else
657 ss << " (Unknown)";
658 if (ConditionMgr::CanHaveSourceGroupSet(SourceType))
659 ss << ", SourceGroup: " << SourceGroup;
660 ss << ", SourceEntry: " << SourceEntry;
661 if (ConditionMgr::CanHaveSourceIdSet(SourceType))
662 ss << ", SourceId: " << SourceId;
663
664 if (ext)
665 {
666 ss << ", ConditionType: " << ConditionType;
667 if (ConditionType < CONDITION_MAX)
668 ss << " (" << ConditionMgr::StaticConditionTypeData[ConditionType].Name << ")";
669 else
670 ss << " (Unknown)";
671 }
672
673 ss << "]";
674 return ss.str();
675}

683
684uint32 ConditionMgr::GetSearcherTypeMaskForConditionList(ConditionContainer const& conditions) const
685{
686 if (conditions.empty())
687 return GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_ALL;
688 // groupId, typeMask
689 std::map<uint32, uint32> elseGroupSearcherTypeMasks;
690 for (ConditionContainer::const_iterator i = conditions.begin(); i != conditions.end(); ++i)
691 {
692 // no point of having not loaded conditions in list
693 ASSERT((*i)->isLoaded() && "ConditionMgr::GetSearcherTypeMaskForConditionList - not yet loaded condition found in list");
694 std::map<uint32, uint32>::const_iterator itr = elseGroupSearcherTypeMasks.find((*i)->ElseGroup);
695 // group not filled yet, fill with widest mask possible
696 if (itr == elseGroupSearcherTypeMasks.end())
697 elseGroupSearcherTypeMasks[(*i)->ElseGroup] = GRID_MAP_TYPE_MASK_ALL;
698 // no point of checking anymore, empty mask
699 else if (!itr->second)
700 continue;
701
702 if ((*i)->ReferenceId) // handle reference
703 {
704 ConditionReferenceContainer::const_iterator ref = ConditionReferenceStore.find((*i)->ReferenceId);
705 ASSERT(ref != ConditionReferenceStore.end() && "ConditionMgr::GetSearcherTypeMaskForConditionList - incorrect reference");
706 elseGroupSearcherTypeMasks[(*i)->ElseGroup] &= GetSearcherTypeMaskForConditionList((*ref).second);
707 }
708 else // handle normal condition
709 {
710 // object will match conditions in one ElseGroupStore only when it matches all of them
711 // so, let's find a smallest possible mask which satisfies all conditions
712 elseGroupSearcherTypeMasks[(*i)->ElseGroup] &= (*i)->GetSearcherTypeMaskForCondition();
713 }
714 }
715 // object will match condition when one of the checks in ElseGroupStore is matching
716 // so, let's include all possible masks
717 uint32 mask = 0;
718 for (std::map<uint32, uint32>::const_iterator i = elseGroupSearcherTypeMasks.begin(); i != elseGroupSearcherTypeMasks.end(); ++i)
719 mask |= i->second;
720
721 return mask;
722}

724bool ConditionMgr::IsObjectMeetToConditionList(ConditionSourceInfo& sourceInfo, ConditionContainer const& conditions) const
725{
726 // groupId, groupCheckPassed
727 std::map<uint32, bool> elseGroupStore;
728 for (Condition const* condition : conditions)
729 {
730 TC_LOG_DEBUG("condition", "ConditionMgr::IsPlayerMeetToConditionList %s val1: %u", condition->ToString().c_str(), condition->ConditionValue1);
731 if (condition->isLoaded())
732 {
733 //! Find ElseGroup in ElseGroupStore
734 std::map<uint32, bool>::const_iterator itr = elseGroupStore.find(condition->ElseGroup);
735 //! If not found, add an entry in the store and set to true (placeholder)
736 if (itr == elseGroupStore.end())
737 elseGroupStore[condition->ElseGroup] = true;
738 else if (!(*itr).second)
739 continue;
740
741 if (condition->ReferenceId)//handle reference
742 {
743 ConditionReferenceContainer::const_iterator ref = ConditionReferenceStore.find(condition->ReferenceId);
744 if (ref != ConditionReferenceStore.end())
745 {
746 if (!IsObjectMeetToConditionList(sourceInfo, ref->second))
747 elseGroupStore[condition->ElseGroup] = false;
748 }
749 else
750 {
751 TC_LOG_DEBUG("condition", "ConditionMgr::IsPlayerMeetToConditionList %s Reference template -%u not found",
752 condition->ToString().c_str(), condition->ReferenceId); // checked at loading, should never happen
753 }
754
755 }
756 else //handle normal condition
757 {
758 if (!condition->Meets(sourceInfo))
759 elseGroupStore[condition->ElseGroup] = false;
760 }
761 }
762 }
763 for (std::map<uint32, bool>::const_iterator i = elseGroupStore.begin(); i != elseGroupStore.end(); ++i)
764 if (i->second)
765 return true;
766
767 return false;
768}

928
929void ConditionMgr::LoadConditions(bool isReload)
930{
931 uint32 oldMSTime = getMSTime();
932
933 Clean();
934
935 //must clear all custom handled cases (groupped types) before reload
936 if (isReload)
937 {
938 TC_LOG_INFO("misc", "Reseting Loot Conditions...");
939 LootTemplates_Creature.ResetConditions();
940 LootTemplates_Fishing.ResetConditions();
941 LootTemplates_Gameobject.ResetConditions();
942 LootTemplates_Item.ResetConditions();
943 LootTemplates_Mail.ResetConditions();
944 LootTemplates_Milling.ResetConditions();
945 LootTemplates_Pickpocketing.ResetConditions();
946 LootTemplates_Reference.ResetConditions();
947 LootTemplates_Skinning.ResetConditions();
948 LootTemplates_Disenchant.ResetConditions();
949 LootTemplates_Prospecting.ResetConditions();
950 LootTemplates_Spell.ResetConditions();
951
952 TC_LOG_INFO("misc", "Re-Loading `gossip_menu` Table for Conditions!");
953 sObjectMgr->LoadGossipMenu();
954
955 TC_LOG_INFO("misc", "Re-Loading `gossip_menu_option` Table for Conditions!");
956 sObjectMgr->LoadGossipMenuItems();
957
958 sSpellMgr->UnloadSpellInfoImplicitTargetConditionLists();
959
960 TC_LOG_INFO("misc", "Re-Loading `terrain_phase_info` Table for Conditions!");
961 sObjectMgr->LoadTerrainPhaseInfo();
962
963 TC_LOG_INFO("misc", "Re-Loading `terrain_swap_defaults` Table for Conditions!");
964 sObjectMgr->LoadTerrainSwapDefaults();
965
966 TC_LOG_INFO("misc", "Re-Loading `terrain_worldmap` Table for Conditions!");
967 sObjectMgr->LoadTerrainWorldMaps();
968
969 TC_LOG_INFO("misc", "Re-Loading `phase_area` Table for Conditions!");
970 sObjectMgr->LoadAreaPhases();
971 }
972
973 QueryResult result = WorldDatabase.Query("SELECT SourceTypeOrReferenceId, SourceGroup, SourceEntry, SourceId, ElseGroup, ConditionTypeOrReference, ConditionTarget, "
974 " ConditionValue1, ConditionValue2, ConditionValue3, NegativeCondition, ErrorType, ErrorTextId, ScriptName FROM conditions");
975
976 if (!result)
977 {
978 TC_LOG_ERROR("server.loading", ">> Loaded 0 conditions. DB table `conditions` is empty!");
979 return;
980 }
981
982 uint32 count = 0;
983
984 do
985 {
986 Field* fields = result->Fetch();
987
988 Condition* cond = new Condition();
989 int32 iSourceTypeOrReferenceId = fields[0].GetInt32();
990 cond->SourceGroup = fields[1].GetUInt32();
991 cond->SourceEntry = fields[2].GetInt32();
992 cond->SourceId = fields[3].GetInt32();
993 cond->ElseGroup = fields[4].GetUInt32();
994 int32 iConditionTypeOrReference = fields[5].GetInt32();
995 cond->ConditionTarget = fields[6].GetUInt8();
996 cond->ConditionValue1 = fields[7].GetUInt32();
997 cond->ConditionValue2 = fields[8].GetUInt32();
998 cond->ConditionValue3 = fields[9].GetUInt32();
999 cond->NegativeCondition = fields[10].GetBool();
1000 cond->ErrorType = fields[11].GetUInt32();
1001 cond->ErrorTextId = fields[12].GetUInt32();
1002 cond->ScriptId = sObjectMgr->GetScriptId(fields[13].GetString());
1003
1004 if (iConditionTypeOrReference >= 0)
1005 cond->ConditionType = ConditionTypes(iConditionTypeOrReference);
1006
1007 if (iSourceTypeOrReferenceId >= 0)
1008 cond->SourceType = ConditionSourceType(iSourceTypeOrReferenceId);
1009
1010 if (iConditionTypeOrReference < 0)//it has a reference
1011 {
1012 if (iConditionTypeOrReference == iSourceTypeOrReferenceId)//self referencing, skip
1013 {
1014 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Condition reference %i is referencing self, skipped", iSourceTypeOrReferenceId);
1015 delete cond;
1016 continue;
1017 }
1018 cond->ReferenceId = uint32(abs(iConditionTypeOrReference));
1019
1020 const char* rowType = "reference template";
1021 if (iSourceTypeOrReferenceId >= 0)
1022 rowType = "reference";
1023 //check for useless data
1024 if (cond->ConditionTarget)
1025 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Condition %s %i has useless data in ConditionTarget (%u)!", rowType, iSourceTypeOrReferenceId, cond->ConditionTarget);
1026 if (cond->ConditionValue1)
1027 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Condition %s %i has useless data in value1 (%u)!", rowType, iSourceTypeOrReferenceId, cond->ConditionValue1);
1028 if (cond->ConditionValue2)
1029 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Condition %s %i has useless data in value2 (%u)!", rowType, iSourceTypeOrReferenceId, cond->ConditionValue2);
1030 if (cond->ConditionValue3)
1031 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Condition %s %i has useless data in value3 (%u)!", rowType, iSourceTypeOrReferenceId, cond->ConditionValue3);
1032 if (cond->NegativeCondition)
1033 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Condition %s %i has useless data in NegativeCondition (%u)!", rowType, iSourceTypeOrReferenceId, cond->NegativeCondition);
1034 if (cond->SourceGroup && iSourceTypeOrReferenceId < 0)
1035 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Condition %s %i has useless data in SourceGroup (%u)!", rowType, iSourceTypeOrReferenceId, cond->SourceGroup);
1036 if (cond->SourceEntry && iSourceTypeOrReferenceId < 0)
1037 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Condition %s %i has useless data in SourceEntry (%u)!", rowType, iSourceTypeOrReferenceId, cond->SourceEntry);
1038 }
1039 else if (!isConditionTypeValid(cond))//doesn't have reference, validate ConditionType
1040 {
1041 delete cond;
1042 continue;
1043 }
1044
1045 if (iSourceTypeOrReferenceId < 0)//it is a reference template
1046 {
1047 ConditionReferenceStore[std::abs(iSourceTypeOrReferenceId)].push_back(cond);//add to reference storage
1048 ++count;
1049 continue;
1050 }//end of reference templates
1051
1052 //if not a reference and SourceType is invalid, skip
1053 if (iConditionTypeOrReference >= 0 && !isSourceTypeValid(cond))
1054 {
1055 delete cond;
1056 continue;
1057 }
1058
1059 //Grouping is only allowed for some types (loot templates, gossip menus, gossip items)
1060 if (cond->SourceGroup && !CanHaveSourceGroupSet(cond->SourceType))
1061 {
1062 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s has not allowed value of SourceGroup = %u!", cond->ToString().c_str(), cond->SourceGroup);
1063 delete cond;
1064 continue;
1065 }
1066 if (cond->SourceId && !CanHaveSourceIdSet(cond->SourceType))
1067 {
1068 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s has not allowed value of SourceId = %u!", cond->ToString().c_str(), cond->SourceId);
1069 delete cond;
1070 continue;
1071 }
1072
1073 if (cond->ErrorType && cond->SourceType != CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_SPELL)
1074 {
1075 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s can't have ErrorType (%u), set to 0!", cond->ToString().c_str(), cond->ErrorType);
1076 cond->ErrorType = 0;
1077 }
1078
1079 if (cond->ErrorTextId && !cond->ErrorType)
1080 {
1081 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s has any ErrorType, ErrorTextId (%u) is set, set to 0!", cond->ToString().c_str(), cond->ErrorTextId);
1082 cond->ErrorTextId = 0;
1083 }
1084
1085 if (cond->SourceGroup)
1086 {
1087 bool valid = false;
1088 // handle grouped conditions
1089 switch (cond->SourceType)
1090 {
1091 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_CREATURE_LOOT_TEMPLATE:
1092 valid = addToLootTemplate(cond, LootTemplates_Creature.GetLootForConditionFill(cond->SourceGroup));
1093 break;
1094 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_DISENCHANT_LOOT_TEMPLATE:
1095 valid = addToLootTemplate(cond, LootTemplates_Disenchant.GetLootForConditionFill(cond->SourceGroup));
1096 break;
1097 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_FISHING_LOOT_TEMPLATE:
1098 valid = addToLootTemplate(cond, LootTemplates_Fishing.GetLootForConditionFill(cond->SourceGroup));
1099 break;
1100 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_GAMEOBJECT_LOOT_TEMPLATE:
1101 valid = addToLootTemplate(cond, LootTemplates_Gameobject.GetLootForConditionFill(cond->SourceGroup));
1102 break;
1103 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_ITEM_LOOT_TEMPLATE:
1104 valid = addToLootTemplate(cond, LootTemplates_Item.GetLootForConditionFill(cond->SourceGroup));
1105 break;
1106 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_MAIL_LOOT_TEMPLATE:
1107 valid = addToLootTemplate(cond, LootTemplates_Mail.GetLootForConditionFill(cond->SourceGroup));
1108 break;
1109 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_MILLING_LOOT_TEMPLATE:
1110 valid = addToLootTemplate(cond, LootTemplates_Milling.GetLootForConditionFill(cond->SourceGroup));
1111 break;
1112 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_PICKPOCKETING_LOOT_TEMPLATE:
1113 valid = addToLootTemplate(cond, LootTemplates_Pickpocketing.GetLootForConditionFill(cond->SourceGroup));
1114 break;
1115 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_PROSPECTING_LOOT_TEMPLATE:
1116 valid = addToLootTemplate(cond, LootTemplates_Prospecting.GetLootForConditionFill(cond->SourceGroup));
1117 break;
1118 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_REFERENCE_LOOT_TEMPLATE:
1119 valid = addToLootTemplate(cond, LootTemplates_Reference.GetLootForConditionFill(cond->SourceGroup));
1120 break;
1121 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_SKINNING_LOOT_TEMPLATE:
1122 valid = addToLootTemplate(cond, LootTemplates_Skinning.GetLootForConditionFill(cond->SourceGroup));
1123 break;
1124 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_SPELL_LOOT_TEMPLATE:
1125 valid = addToLootTemplate(cond, LootTemplates_Spell.GetLootForConditionFill(cond->SourceGroup));
1126 break;
1127 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_GOSSIP_MENU:
1128 valid = addToGossipMenus(cond);
1129 break;
1130 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_GOSSIP_MENU_OPTION:
1131 valid = addToGossipMenuItems(cond);
1132 break;
1133 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_SPELL_CLICK_EVENT:
1134 {
1135 SpellClickEventConditionStore[cond->SourceGroup][cond->SourceEntry].push_back(cond);
1136 valid = true;
1137 ++count;
1138 continue; // do not add to m_AllocatedMemory to avoid double deleting
1139 }
1140 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_SPELL_IMPLICIT_TARGET:
1141 valid = addToSpellImplicitTargetConditions(cond);
1142 break;
1143 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_VEHICLE_SPELL:
1144 {
1145 VehicleSpellConditionStore[cond->SourceGroup][cond->SourceEntry].push_back(cond);
1146 valid = true;
1147 ++count;
1148 continue; // do not add to m_AllocatedMemory to avoid double deleting
1149 }
1150 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_SMART_EVENT:
1151 {
1152 //! TODO: PAIR_32 ?
1153 std::pair<int32, uint32> key = std::make_pair(cond->SourceEntry, cond->SourceId);
1154 SmartEventConditionStore[key][cond->SourceGroup].push_back(cond);
1155 valid = true;
1156 ++count;
1157 continue;
1158 }
1159 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_NPC_VENDOR:
1160 {
1161 NpcVendorConditionContainerStore[cond->SourceGroup][cond->SourceEntry].push_back(cond);
1162 valid = true;
1163 ++count;
1164 continue;
1165 }
1166 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_PHASE:
1167 valid = addToPhases(cond);
1168 break;
1169 default:
1170 break;
1171 }
1172
1173 if (!valid)
1174 {
1175 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s Not handled grouped condition.", cond->ToString().c_str());
1176 delete cond;
1177 }
1178 else
1179 {
1180 AllocatedMemoryStore.push_back(cond);
1181 ++count;
1182 }
1183 continue;
1184 }
1185
1186 //handle not grouped conditions
1187 //add new Condition to storage based on Type/Entry
1188 ConditionStore[cond->SourceType][cond->SourceEntry].push_back(cond);
1189 ++count;
1190 }
1191 while (result->NextRow());
1192
1193 TC_LOG_INFO("server.loading", ">> Loaded %u conditions in %u ms", count, GetMSTimeDiffToNow(oldMSTime));
1194}
1195
1196bool ConditionMgr::addToLootTemplate(Condition* cond, LootTemplate* loot) const
1197{
1198 if (!loot)
1199 {
1200 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s LootTemplate %u not found.", cond->ToString().c_str(), cond->SourceGroup);
1201 return false;
1202 }
1203
1204 if (loot->addConditionItem(cond))
1205 return true;
1206
1207 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s Item %u not found in LootTemplate %u.", cond->ToString().c_str(), cond->SourceEntry, cond->SourceGroup);
1208 return false;
1209}

1247 return false;
1248}
1249
1250bool ConditionMgr::addToSpellImplicitTargetConditions(Condition* cond) const
1251{
1252 uint32 conditionEffMask = cond->SourceGroup;
1253 SpellInfo* spellInfo = const_cast<SpellInfo*>(sSpellMgr->AssertSpellInfo(cond->SourceEntry));
1254 std::list<uint32> sharedMasks;
1255 for (uint8 i = 0; i < MAX_SPELL_EFFECTS; ++i)
1256 {
1257 SpellEffectInfo const* effect = spellInfo->GetEffect(DIFFICULTY_NONE, i);
1258 if (!effect)
1259 continue;
1260
1261 // check if effect is already a part of some shared mask
1262 bool found = false;
1263 for (std::list<uint32>::iterator itr = sharedMasks.begin(); itr != sharedMasks.end(); ++itr)
1264 {
1265 if ((1 << i) & *itr)
1266 {
1267 found = true;
1268 break;
1269 }
1270 }
1271
1272 if (found)
1273 continue;
1274
1275 // build new shared mask with found effect
1276 uint32 sharedMask = 1 << i;
1277 ConditionContainer* cmp = effect->ImplicitTargetConditions;
1278 for (uint8 effIndex = i + 1; effIndex < MAX_SPELL_EFFECTS; ++effIndex)
1279 {
1280 SpellEffectInfo const* inner = spellInfo->GetEffect(DIFFICULTY_NONE, effIndex);
1281 if (!inner)
1282 continue;
1283
1284 if (inner->ImplicitTargetConditions == cmp)
1285 sharedMask |= 1 << effIndex;
1286 }
1287
1288 sharedMasks.push_back(sharedMask);
1289 }
1290
1291 for (std::list<uint32>::iterator itr = sharedMasks.begin(); itr != sharedMasks.end(); ++itr)
1292 {
1293 // some effect indexes should have same data
1294 if (uint32 commonMask = *itr & conditionEffMask)
1295 {
1296 uint8 firstEffIndex = 0;
1297 for (; firstEffIndex < MAX_SPELL_EFFECTS; ++firstEffIndex)
1298 if ((1<<firstEffIndex) & *itr)
1299 break;
1300
1301 if (firstEffIndex >= MAX_SPELL_EFFECTS)
1302 return false;
1303
1304 SpellEffectInfo const* effect = spellInfo->GetEffect(DIFFICULTY_NONE, firstEffIndex);
1305 if (!effect)
1306 continue;
1307
1308 // get shared data
1309 ConditionContainer* sharedList = effect->ImplicitTargetConditions;
1310
1311 // there's already data entry for that sharedMask
1312 if (sharedList)
1313 {
1314 // we have overlapping masks in db
1315 if (conditionEffMask != *itr)
1316 {
1317 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s in `condition` table, has incorrect SourceGroup %u (spell effectMask) set - "
1318 "effect masks are overlapping (all SourceGroup values having given bit set must be equal) - ignoring.", cond->ToString().c_str(), cond->SourceGroup);
1319 return false;
1320 }
1321 }
1322 // no data for shared mask, we can create new submask
1323 else
1324 {
1325 // add new list, create new shared mask
1326 sharedList = new ConditionContainer();
1327 bool assigned = false;
1328 for (uint8 i = firstEffIndex; i < MAX_SPELL_EFFECTS; ++i)
1329 {
1330 SpellEffectInfo const* eff = spellInfo->GetEffect(DIFFICULTY_NONE, i);
1331 if (!eff)
1332 continue;
1333
1334 if ((1 << i) & commonMask)
1335 {
1336 const_cast<SpellEffectInfo*>(eff)->ImplicitTargetConditions = sharedList;
1337 assigned = true;
1338 }
1339 }
1340
1341 if (!assigned)
1342 {
1343 delete sharedList;
1344 break;
1345 }
1346 }
1347 sharedList->push_back(cond);
1348 break;
1349 }
1350 }
1351 return true;
1352}
1353
1354bool ConditionMgr::addToPhases(Condition* cond) const
1355{
1356 if (!cond->SourceEntry)
1357 {
1358 PhaseInfo& p = sObjectMgr->GetAreaPhasesForLoading();
1359 for (auto phaseItr = p.begin(); phaseItr != p.end(); ++phaseItr)
1360 {
1361 for (PhaseInfoStruct& phase : phaseItr->second)
1362 {
1363 if (phase.Id == cond->SourceGroup)
1364 {
1365 phase.Conditions.push_back(cond);
1366 return true;
1367 }
1368 }
1369 }
1370 }
1371 else if (std::vector<PhaseInfoStruct>* phases = sObjectMgr->GetPhasesForAreaForLoading(cond->SourceEntry))
1372 {
1373 for (PhaseInfoStruct& phase : *phases)
1374 {
1375 if (phase.Id == cond->SourceGroup)
1376 {
1377 phase.Conditions.push_back(cond);
1378 return true;
1379 }
1380 }
1381 }
1382
1383 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s Area %u does not have phase %u.", cond->ToString().c_str(), cond->SourceGroup, cond->SourceEntry);
1384 return false;
1385}

1607 return false;

1610 if ((cond->SourceGroup > MAX_EFFECT_MASK) || !cond->SourceGroup)
1611 {

1613 return false;
1614 }
1615
1616 uint32 origGroup = cond->SourceGroup;
1617
1618 for (uint8 i = 0; i < MAX_SPELL_EFFECTS; ++i)
1619 {
1620 if (!((1 << i) & cond->SourceGroup))
1621 continue;
1622
1623 SpellEffectInfo const* effect = spellInfo->GetEffect(DIFFICULTY_NONE, i);
1624 if (!effect)
1625 continue;
1626
1627 if (effect->ChainTargets > 0)
1628 continue;
1629
1630 switch (effect->TargetA.GetSelectionCategory())
1631 {
1632 case TARGET_SELECT_CATEGORY_NEARBY:
1633 case TARGET_SELECT_CATEGORY_CONE:
1634 case TARGET_SELECT_CATEGORY_AREA:
1635 continue;
1636 default:
1637 break;
1638 }
1639
1640 switch (effect->TargetB.GetSelectionCategory())
1641 {
1642 case TARGET_SELECT_CATEGORY_NEARBY:
1643 case TARGET_SELECT_CATEGORY_CONE:
1644 case TARGET_SELECT_CATEGORY_AREA:
1645 continue;
1646 default:
1647 break;
1648 }
1649
1650 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "SourceEntry %u SourceGroup %u in `condition` table - spell %u does not have implicit targets of types: _AREA_, _CONE_, _NEARBY_, __CHAIN__ for effect %u, SourceGroup needs correction, ignoring.", cond->SourceEntry, origGroup, cond->SourceEntry, uint32(i));
1651 cond->SourceGroup &= ~(1 << i);
1652 }
1653 // all effects were removed, no need to add the condition at all
1654 if (!cond->SourceGroup)
1655 return false;
1656 break;
1657 }
1658 case CONDITION_SOURCE_TYPE_CREATURE_TEMPLATE_VEHICLE:
1659 {

1661 {

1685 break;

1698 break;

1700 if (!sObjectMgr->GetCreatureTemplate(cond->SourceGroup))

1717 return false;

1719 ItemTemplate const* itemTemplate = sObjectMgr->GetItemTemplate(cond->SourceEntry);
1720 if (!itemTemplate)

1755
1756bool ConditionMgr::isConditionTypeValid(Condition* cond) const
1757{
1758 if (cond->ConditionType == CONDITION_NONE || cond->ConditionType >= CONDITION_MAX)
1759 {
1760 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s Invalid ConditionType in `condition` table, ignoring.", cond->ToString().c_str());
1761 return false;
1762 }
1763
1764 if (cond->ConditionTarget >= cond->GetMaxAvailableConditionTargets())
1765 {
1766 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s in `condition` table, has incorrect ConditionTarget set, ignoring.", cond->ToString(true).c_str());
1767 return false;
1768 }
1769
1770 switch (cond->ConditionType)
1771 {
1772 case CONDITION_AURA:
1773 {
1774 if (!sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(cond->ConditionValue1))
1775 {
1776 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s has non existing spell (Id: %d), skipped.", cond->ToString(true).c_str(), cond->ConditionValue1);
1777 return false;
1778 }
1779
1780 if (cond->ConditionValue2 > EFFECT_2)
1781 {
1782 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s has non existing effect index (%u) (must be 0..2), skipped.", cond->ToString(true).c_str(), cond->ConditionValue2);
1783 return false;
1784 }
1785 break;
1786 }
1787 case CONDITION_ITEM:
1788 {
1789 ItemTemplate const* proto = sObjectMgr->GetItemTemplate(cond->ConditionValue1);
1790 if (!proto)
1791 {
1792 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s Item (%u) does not exist, skipped.", cond->ToString(true).c_str(), cond->ConditionValue1);
1793 return false;
1794 }
1795
1796 if (!cond->ConditionValue2)
1797 {
1798 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s Zero item count in ConditionValue2, skipped.", cond->ToString(true).c_str());
1799 return false;
1800 }
1801 break;
1802 }
1803 case CONDITION_ITEM_EQUIPPED:
1804 {
1805 ItemTemplate const* proto = sObjectMgr->GetItemTemplate(cond->ConditionValue1);
1806 if (!proto)
1807 {
1808 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s Item (%u) does not exist, skipped.", cond->ToString(true).c_str(), cond->ConditionValue1);
1809 return false;
1810 }
1811 break;
1812 }
1813 case CONDITION_ZONEID:
1814 {
1815 AreaTableEntry const* areaEntry = sAreaTableStore.LookupEntry(cond->ConditionValue1);
1816 if (!areaEntry)
1817 {
1818 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s Area (%u) does not exist, skipped.", cond->ToString(true).c_str(), cond->ConditionValue1);
1819 return false;
1820 }
1821
1822 if (areaEntry->ParentAreaID != 0)
1823 {
1824 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s requires to be in area (%u) which is a subzone but zone expected, skipped.", cond->ToString(true).c_str(), cond->ConditionValue1);
1825 return false;
1826 }
1827 break;
1828 }
1829 case CONDITION_REPUTATION_RANK:
1830 {
1831 FactionEntry const* factionEntry = sFactionStore.LookupEntry(cond->ConditionValue1);
1832 if (!factionEntry)
1833 {
1834 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s has non existing faction (%u), skipped.", cond->ToString(true).c_str(), cond->ConditionValue1);
1835 return false;
1836 }
1837 break;
1838 }
1839 case CONDITION_TEAM:
1840 {
1841 if (cond->ConditionValue1 != ALLIANCE && cond->ConditionValue1 != HORDE)
1842 {
1843 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s specifies unknown team (%u), skipped.", cond->ToString(true).c_str(), cond->ConditionValue1);
1844 return false;
1845 }
1846 break;
1847 }
1848 case CONDITION_SKILL:
1849 {
1850 SkillLineEntry const* pSkill = sSkillLineStore.LookupEntry(cond->ConditionValue1);
1851 if (!pSkill)
1852 {
1853 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s specifies non-existing skill (%u), skipped.", cond->ToString(true).c_str(), cond->ConditionValue1);
1854 return false;
1855 }
1856
1857 if (cond->ConditionValue2 < 1 || cond->ConditionValue2 > sWorld->GetConfigMaxSkillValue())
1858 {
1859 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s specifies skill (%u) with invalid value (%u), skipped.", cond->ToString(true).c_str(), cond->ConditionValue1, cond->ConditionValue2);
1860 return false;
1861 }
1862 break;
1863 }
1864 case CONDITION_QUESTREWARDED:
1865 case CONDITION_QUESTTAKEN:
1866 case CONDITION_QUEST_NONE:
1867 case CONDITION_QUEST_COMPLETE:
1868 {
1869 if (!sObjectMgr->GetQuestTemplate(cond->ConditionValue1))
1870 {
1871 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s points to non-existing quest (%u), skipped.", cond->ToString(true).c_str(), cond->ConditionValue1);
1872 return false;
1873 }
1874 break;
1875 }
1876 case CONDITION_ACTIVE_EVENT:
1877 {
1878 GameEventMgr::GameEventDataMap const& events = sGameEventMgr->GetEventMap();
1879 if (cond->ConditionValue1 >= events.size() || !events[cond->ConditionValue1].isValid())
1880 {
1881 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s has non existing event id (%u), skipped.", cond->ToString(true).c_str(), cond->ConditionValue1);
1882 return false;
1883 }
1884 break;
1885 }
1886 case CONDITION_ACHIEVEMENT:
1887 {
1888 AchievementEntry const* achievement = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievement(cond->ConditionValue1);
1889 if (!achievement)
1890 {
1891 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s has non existing achivement id (%u), skipped.", cond->ToString(true).c_str(), cond->ConditionValue1);
1892 return false;
1893 }
1894 break;
1895 }
1896 case CONDITION_CLASS:
1897 {
1898 if (!(cond->ConditionValue1 & CLASSMASK_ALL_PLAYABLE))
1899 {
1900 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s has non existing classmask (%u), skipped.", cond->ToString(true).c_str(), cond->ConditionValue1 & ~CLASSMASK_ALL_PLAYABLE);
1901 return false;
1902 }
1903 break;
1904 }
1905 case CONDITION_RACE:
1906 {
1907 if (!(cond->ConditionValue1 & RACEMASK_ALL_PLAYABLE))
1908 {
1909 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "%s has non existing racemask (%u), skipped.", cond->ToString(true).c_str(), cond->ConditionValue1 & ~RACEMASK_ALL_PLAYABLE);
1910 return false;

2271
2272inline bool PlayerConditionCompare(int32 comparisonType, int32 value1, int32 value2)
2273{
2274 switch (comparisonType)
2275 {
2276 case 1:
2277 return value1 == value2;
2278 case 2:
2279 return value1 != value2;
2280 case 3:
2281 return value1 > value2;
2282 case 4:
2283 return value1 >= value2;
2284 case 5:
2285 return value1 < value2;
2286 case 6:
2287 return value1 <= value2;
2288 default:
2289 break;
2290 }
2291 return false;
2292}
2293
2294template<std::size_t N>
2295inline bool PlayerConditionLogic(uint32 logic, std::array<bool, N>& results)
2296{
2297 static_assert(N < 16, "Logic array size must be equal to or less than 16");
2298
2299 for (std::size_t i = 0; i < results.size(); ++i)
2300 if ((logic >> (16 + i)) & 1)
2301 results[i] ^= true;
2302
2303 bool result = results[0];
2304 for (std::size_t i = 1; i < results.size(); ++i)
2305 {
2306 switch ((logic >> (2 * (i - 1))) & 3)
2307 {
2308 case 1:
2309 result = result && results[i];
2310 break;
2311 case 2:
2312 result = result || results[i];
2313 break;
2314 default:
2315 break;
2316 }
2317 }
2318
2319 return result;
2320}
2321
2322bool ConditionMgr::IsPlayerMeetingCondition(Player* player, PlayerConditionEntry const* condition)
2323{
2324 if (condition->MinLevel && player->getLevel() < condition->MinLevel)
2325 return false;
2326
2327 if (condition->MaxLevel && player->getLevel() > condition->MaxLevel)
2328 return false;
2329
2330 if (condition->RaceMask && !(player->getRaceMask() & condition->RaceMask))
2331 return false;
2332
2333 if (condition->ClassMask && !(player->getClassMask() & condition->ClassMask))
2334 return false;
2335
2336 if (condition->Gender >= 0 && player->getGender() != condition->Gender)
2337 return false;
2338
2339 if (condition->NativeGender >= 0 && player->GetByteValue(PLAYER_BYTES_3, PLAYER_BYTES_3_OFFSET_GENDER) != condition->NativeGender)
2340 return false;
2341
2342 if (condition->PowerType != -1 && condition->PowerTypeComp)
2343 {
2344 int32 requiredPowerValue = condition->Flags & 4 ? player->GetMaxPower(Powers(condition->PowerType)) : condition->PowerTypeValue;
2345 if (!PlayerConditionCompare(condition->PowerTypeComp, player->GetPower(Powers(condition->PowerType)), requiredPowerValue))
2346 return false;
2347 }
2348
2349 if (condition->ChrSpecializationIndex >= 0 || condition->ChrSpecializationRole >= 0)
2350 {
2351 if (ChrSpecializationEntry const* spec = sChrSpecializationStore.LookupEntry(player->GetSpecId(player->GetActiveTalentGroup())))
2352 {
2353 if (condition->ChrSpecializationIndex >= 0 && spec->OrderIndex != uint32(condition->ChrSpecializationIndex))
2354 return false;
2355
2356 if (condition->ChrSpecializationRole >= 0 && spec->Role != uint32(condition->ChrSpecializationRole))
2357 return false;
2358 }
2359 }
2360
2361 if (condition->SkillID[0] || condition->SkillID[1] || condition->SkillID[2] || condition->SkillID[3])
2362 {
2363 using SkillCount = std::extent<decltype(condition->SkillID)>;
2364
2365 std::array<bool, SkillCount::value> results;
2366 results.fill(true);
2367 for (std::size_t i = 0; i < SkillCount::value; ++i)
2368 {
2369 if (condition->SkillID[i])
2370 {
2371 uint16 skillValue = player->GetSkillValue(condition->SkillID[i]);
2372 results[i] = skillValue != 0 && skillValue > condition->MinSkill[i] && skillValue < condition->MaxSkill[i];
2373 }
2374 }
2375
2376 if (!PlayerConditionLogic(condition->SkillLogic, results))
2377 return false;
2378 }
2379
2380 if (condition->LanguageID)
2381 {
2382 if (LanguageDesc const* lang = GetLanguageDescByID(condition->LanguageID))
2383 {
2384 uint32 languageSkill = player->GetSkillValue(lang->skill_id);
2385 if (!languageSkill && player->HasAuraTypeWithMiscvalue(SPELL_AURA_COMPREHEND_LANGUAGE, condition->LanguageID))
2386 languageSkill = 300;
2387
2388 if (condition->MinLanguage && languageSkill < condition->MinLanguage)
2389 return false;
2390
2391 if (condition->MaxLanguage && languageSkill > condition->MaxLanguage)
2392 return false;
2393 }
2394 }
2395
2396 if (condition->MinFactionID[0] && condition->MinFactionID[1] && condition->MinFactionID[2] && condition->MaxFactionID)
2397 {
2398 if (!condition->MinFactionID[0] && !condition->MinFactionID[1] && !condition->MinFactionID[2])
2399 {
2400 if (ReputationRank const* forcedRank = player->GetReputationMgr().GetForcedRankIfAny(condition->MaxFactionID))
2401 {
2402 if (*forcedRank > ReputationRank(condition->MaxReputation))
2403 return false;
2404 }
2405 else if (player->GetReputationRank(condition->MaxFactionID) > ReputationRank(condition->MaxReputation))
2406 return false;
2407 }
2408 else
2409 {
2410 using FactionCount = std::extent<decltype(condition->MinFactionID)>;
2411
2412 std::array<bool, FactionCount::value + 1> results;
2413 results.fill(true);
2414 for (std::size_t i = 0; i < FactionCount::value; ++i)
2415 {
2416 if (condition->MinFactionID[i])
2417 {
2418 if (ReputationRank const* forcedRank = player->GetReputationMgr().GetForcedRankIfAny(condition->MinFactionID[i]))
2419 results[i] = *forcedRank >= ReputationRank(condition->MinReputation[i]);
2420 else
2421 results[i] = player->GetReputationRank(condition->MinFactionID[i]) >= ReputationRank(condition->MinReputation[i]);
2422 }
2423 }
2424
2425 if (ReputationRank const* forcedRank = player->GetReputationMgr().GetForcedRankIfAny(condition->MaxFactionID))
2426 results[3] = *forcedRank <= ReputationRank(condition->MaxReputation);
2427 else
2428 results[3] = player->GetReputationRank(condition->MaxFactionID) <= ReputationRank(condition->MaxReputation);
2429
2430 if (!PlayerConditionLogic(condition->ReputationLogic, results))
2431 return false;
2432 }
2433 }
2434
2435 if (condition->PvpMedal && !((1 << (condition->PvpMedal - 1)) & player->GetUInt32Value(PLAYER_FIELD_PVP_MEDALS)))
2436 return false;
2437
2438 if (condition->LifetimeMaxPVPRank && player->GetByteValue(PLAYER_FIELD_BYTES, PLAYER_FIELD_BYTES_OFFSET_LIFETIME_MAX_PVP_RANK) != condition->LifetimeMaxPVPRank)
2439 return false;
2440
2441 if (condition->PartyStatus)
2442 {
2443 Group* group = player->GetGroup();
2444 switch (condition->PartyStatus)
2445 {
2446 case 1:
2447 if (group)
2448 return false;
2449 break;
2450 case 2:
2451 if (!group)
2452 return false;
2453 break;
2454 case 3:
2455 if (!group || group->isRaidGroup())
2456 return false;
2457 break;
2458 case 4:
2459 if (!group || !group->isRaidGroup())
2460 return false;
2461 break;
2462 case 5:
2463 if (group && group->isRaidGroup())
2464 return false;
2465 break;
2466 default:
2467 break;
2468 }
2469 }
2470
2471 if (condition->PrevQuestID[0])
2472 {
2473 using PrevQuestCount = std::extent<decltype(condition->PrevQuestID)>;
2474

2476 results.fill(true);
2477 for (std::size_t i = 0; i < PrevQuestCount::value; ++i)
2478 if (uint32 questBit = sDB2Manager.GetQuestUniqueBitFlag(condition->PrevQuestID[i]))
2479 results[i] = (player->GetUInt32Value(PLAYER_FIELD_QUEST_COMPLETED + ((questBit - 1) >> 5)) & (1 << ((questBit - 1) & 31))) != 0;
2480

2482 return false;
2483 }
2484
2485 if (condition->CurrQuestID[0])
2486 {
2487 using CurrQuestCount = std::extent<decltype(condition->CurrQuestID)>;

2490 results.fill(true);
2491 for (std::size_t i = 0; i < CurrQuestCount::value; ++i)
2492 if (condition->CurrQuestID[i])
2493 results[i] = player->FindQuestSlot(condition->CurrQuestID[i]) != MAX_QUEST_LOG_SIZE;

2499 if (condition->CurrentCompletedQuestID[0])
2500 {

2504 results.fill(true);

2623 return false;

2626 return false;
2627
2628 if (condition->MinExpansionLevel != -1 && condition->MinExpansionTier != -1 && !player->IsGameMaster()
2629 && ((condition->MinExpansionLevel == int32(sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_EXPANSION)) && condition->MinExpansionTier > 0) /*TODO: implement tier*/
2630 || condition->MinExpansionLevel > int32(sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_EXPANSION))))
2631 return false;

2634 return false;

2639 if (!Trinity::Containers::Intersects(phases.begin(), phases.end(), player->GetPhases().begin(), player->GetPhases().end()))
2640 return false;

2644 {
2645 Quest const* quest = sObjectMgr->GetQuestTemplate(condition->QuestKillID);
2646 if (quest && player->GetQuestStatus(condition->QuestKillID) != QUEST_STATUS_COMPLETE)

2648 using QuestKillCount = std::extent<decltype(condition->QuestKillMonster)>;
2649
2650 std::array<bool, QuestKillCount::value> results;

2657 {
2658 return objective.Type == QUEST_OBJECTIVE_MONSTER && uint32(objective.ObjectID) == condition->QuestKillMonster[i];
2659 });
2660 if (objectiveItr != quest->GetObjectives().end())
2661 results[i] = player->GetQuestObjectiveData(quest, objectiveItr->StorageIndex) >= objectiveItr->Amount;
2662 }

2666 return false;
2667 }
2668 }
2669
2670 if (condition->MinAvgItemLevel && uint32(std::floor(player->GetFloatValue(PLAYER_FIELD_AVG_ITEM_LEVEL))) < condition->MinAvgItemLevel)
2671 return false;
2672
2673 if (condition->MaxAvgItemLevel && uint32(std::floor(player->GetFloatValue(PLAYER_FIELD_AVG_ITEM_LEVEL))) > condition->MaxAvgItemLevel)
2674 return false;
2675
2676 if (condition->MinAvgEquippedItemLevel && uint32(std::floor(player->GetFloatValue(PLAYER_FIELD_AVG_ITEM_LEVEL + 1))) < condition->MinAvgEquippedItemLevel)
2677 return false;
2678
2679 if (condition->MaxAvgEquippedItemLevel && uint32(std::floor(player->GetFloatValue(PLAYER_FIELD_AVG_ITEM_LEVEL + 1))) > condition->MaxAvgEquippedItemLevel)
